<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"></span></strong></p>
<p><strong>After 20 years in the United States, Han returned to China to open a studio in Beijing. Surrounded by the countryside, the studio is the perfect place to develop works that reflect both the gritty realities of urban life and the serenity of the nature.</strong></p>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Solo Exhibitions</span></strong> <br>
