1996 From Mao to Now, Mandarin Oriental Fine Arts, Mandarin Oriental Hotel, Hong Kong <br>
1995 Contrast, Michaelian-Kohlberg Gallery, New York, USA <br>
1994 New York, New York, Gallery V, Columbus, Ohio, USA <br>
1993 Sounds of Nature, Gallery V, Columbus, Ohio, USA <br>
Visions, Delaware County Cultural Arts Centre, Delaware, Ohio, USA <br>
Thinking of Today, Ohio State University, Columbus, Ohio, USA <br>
<br>
